module: b1-35
level: B1
sequence: 35
slug: concessive-khocha
version: '2.0'
title: 'Допустові речення: хоча, незважаючи на'
subtitle: Concessive Clauses - Although, Despite
content_outline:
- section: 'Тест: Перевірте себе'
  points:
  - Diagnostic quiz on concessive clauses
  - Self-assessment questions — focus on distinguishing 'незважаючи на' vs common
    error 'не дивлячись на'
- section: Пояснення
  points:
  - 'What are concessive clauses — State Standard §4.4.3: complex sentences with concessive
    subordinate clauses'
  - 'хоча - Although Clauses — use high-freq collocations ''хоча б'', ''хоча й'';
    cultural hook: proverb «Хоч бачить око, та зуб не йме»'
  - 'незважаючи на - Despite — learner error: calque ''не дивлячись на'' (gerund)
    vs ''незважаючи на'' (preposition); spelling warning: ''не зважаючи'' (2 words,
    gerund) vs ''незважаючи'' (1 word, prep)'
  - 'Other Concessive Connectors (попри, хоч би) — ''попри'' as stylish media alternative;
    literature quote: Ліна Костенко «Не бійся правди, хоч яка гірка...»'
  - Concessive vs Adversative (хоча vs але) — introduction of 'проте' as formal/academic
    connector
- section: Практика
  points:
  - Form concessive clauses — practice transforming 'але' sentences into 'хоча' clauses
  - 'Express unexpected outcomes — folk wisdom: «Хоч не з красою, аби з головою»'
- section: Діалоги
  points:
  - 'Concessive clauses in conversation — register mismatch warning: avoid archaic
    ''дарма що'' in business contexts'
  - Contrast scenarios
vocabulary_hints:
  required:
  - хоча (although) — хоча б (at least), хоча й (even though), хоча... але/проте
  - незважаючи на (despite) — незважаючи на те що, незважаючи ні на що; NEVER 'не
    дивлячись на'
  - попри (despite - literary) — попри все, попри очікування, попри те що
  - контраст (contrast)
  - неочікуваний (unexpected)
  - результат (result)
  - допустовий (concessive)
  - проте (however) — однак проте, хоча... проте (formal/academic)
  recommended:
  - хоч би (even though) — emphatic concession
  - дарма що (in vain) — archaic/literary usage
  - все одно (anyway)
  - тим не менш (nevertheless)
activity_hints:
- type: fill-in
  focus: Complete concessive sentences
  items: 25
- type: fill-in
  focus: Convert sentences to concessive
  items: 20
- type: error-correction
  focus: Fix concessive clause errors
  items: 15
- type: translate
  focus: English to Ukrainian
  items: 15
focus: grammar
pedagogy: TTT
prerequisites:
- b1-34 (Checkpoint Complex Sentences 1)
connects_to:
- b1-36 (Causal Result Clauses)
objectives:
- Learner understands concessive clause constructions
- Learner can express contrast and unexpected outcomes
- Learner can use various concessive connectors
- Learner can distinguish concessive from adversative clauses
grammar:
- Concessive clauses with хоча (although)
- Concessive phrases with незважаючи на (despite)
- Contrast and unexpected outcome expressions
register: розмовний
phase: B1.3b [Complex Sentences]
persona:
  voice: Senior Language & Culture Specialist
  role: Debate Champion
word_target: 4000
